title: Air Force: Missile Evasion Fighter Jet

creator: Lucky Potion
descriptionHtml:
Air Force missile evasion fighter jet plane is a 2D arcade survival game where you evade missiles and rockets using easy one finger controls.

Easy to use one hand controls and vertical screen orientation are suitable for any environment and make the Air Force a great time killer.

Experience awesome features in the game:

- Control fighter jet plane and escape, dodge or explode all missiles
- One hand game controls in portrait vertical mode
- Clear game user interface
- 3D model of an fighter jet airplane
- Collect stars to increase your score multiplier
- Use Power-UPs like Shield or E.M.P. to protect yourself or destroy all missiles
- Avoid the missiles and guide them into air collisions resulting in an epic explosions
- Compete with friends and people around the world for highest score

Can you handle the super speed of the fighter plane and escape enough missiles to get your way to the top of the Google Play Games leaderboard?
descriptionShort: Avoid missiles and collect stars to get the highest score!
